            <div class="tab_b_inner">
                <span class="course_brief_t">课程简介</span>
                <div class="course_brief">
                        <p><p>
	<span></span><span style="font-size:14px;"> </span> 
</p>
<p>
	1. Topic: COVID-19 Prevention and Treatment Program of China,
TCM And Hubei Province
</p>
<p>
	&nbsp; 演讲题目：新型冠状病毒肺炎的防治—中国方案、中医方案、湖北方案
</p>
<p>
	2. Language: Chinese&nbsp;&nbsp;
Simultaneous interpretation: Chinese to English
</p>
<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">
	演讲语言：中文&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 同声传译：中译英
</p>
<p>
	3. Lecturer: Ba
Yuanming, chief physician at Hubei Provincial Hospital of TCM, professor and
doctoral supervisor, vice director of Great Physician Research Branch of China
Association of Chinese Medicine. He enjoys a special government subsidy of the
State Council and is among the first batch of national excellent clinical
talents of TCM and the sixth batch of instructors on inheritance of TCM
expert’s academic experience. He is an expert of the scientific research team
of Hubei Provincial Headquarters on Epidemic Prevention and Control and is
engaged in kidney disease prevention and control as well as TCM inheritance and
innovation.
</p>
<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">
	演讲嘉宾：巴元明，湖北省中医院主任医师、二级教授，博士生导师。中华中医药学会名医学术研究分会副主任委员，享受国务院政府特殊津贴，首批全国优秀中医临床人才，第六批全国老中医药专家学术经验指导老师。湖北省疫情防控指挥部科研攻关组专家。从事肾脏病防治及中医药传承创新工作。
</p>
<p>
	4. Abstract:
COVID-19, a Public Health Emergency of International Concern, is affecting China
and the entire world. The campaign against COVID-19 in China has achieved significant
results due to the mobilization of the Party and the whole country, and the
unique medical system<span>—</span>diagnosis and treatment mode of
integrated traditional Chinese and Western medicine. In this context, this lecture
focuses on COVID-19 prevention and treatment program of China, TCM and Hubei
Province, providing reference in fighting against the epidemic.
</p>
<p style="text-indent:10.5pt;">
	演讲内容：新型冠状病毒肺炎(COVID-19)作为重大突发公共卫生事件已影响全国乃至全球。目前，中国疫情防控阻击战取得重大战略成果！这离不开全党动员全国动员，以及中国拥有的独特医疗体系—中西医结合的诊疗模式。因此，本次汇报主要讲述新冠肺炎防治的中国方案，中医方案和湖北方案，从而为打好抗“疫”持久战提供借鉴。
</p>
<p>
	<strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><br />
</span></strong> 
</p>
<p>
	<strong><span style="font-size:16px;">相关数据库推荐（Related database）</span></strong> 
</p>
